---
// About section - company description, mission/vision, stat counters
---

<section class="about section" id="nosotros" aria-label="Sobre ARYNSA">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Top decorative line -->
    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Left: Content -->
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-label reveal">Sobre Nosotros</p>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal delay-100">
          Más de una Década<br />
          Construyendo <span>Confianza</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="about-text reveal delay-200">
          <p>
            ARYNSA es una empresa peruana especializada en construcción, consultoría técnica y gestión de proyectos.
            Nacimos con la convicción de que cada obra es una oportunidad para dejar una huella positiva en el país,
            combinando la precisión técnica con la innovación y el compromiso humano.
          </p>
          <p>
            Nuestro equipo multidisciplinario de ingenieros, arquitectos y especialistas trabaja bajo los más altos
            estándares de calidad, garantizando resultados que superan las expectativas de nuestros clientes en cada
            proyecto que emprendemos.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission & Vision cards -->
        <div class="mv-grid reveal delay-300">
          <div class="mv-card">
            <div class="mv-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="mv-card__title">Misión</h3>
              <p class="mv-card__text">
                Brindar soluciones integrales de construcción y consultoría con excelencia técnica, cumplimiento de
                plazos y estándares de calidad que generen valor sostenible para nuestros clientes y la sociedad.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mv-card">
            <div class="mv-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="mv-card__title">Visión</h3>
              <p class="mv-card__text">
                Ser la empresa de construcción y consultoría de referencia en el Perú, reconocida por nuestra
                innovación, integridad y capacidad de transformar proyectos en obras emblemáticas de calidad mundial.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Visual + Stats -->
      <div class="about-visual reveal-right">
        <!-- Main visual block -->
        <div class="about-visual__main">
          <div class="about-visual__inner">
            <div class="about-visual__pattern" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="about-visual__accent-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>

            <div class="about-feature-list">
              {[
                { icon: 'check', text: 'RNP y OSCE registrados' },
                { icon: 'check', text: 'ISO 9001 en procesos de calidad' },
                { icon: 'check', text: 'Personal certificado en BIM y Lean' },
                { icon: 'check', text: 'Cobertura en todo el Perú' },
                { icon: 'check', text: 'Gestión de proyectos PMBOK' },
                { icon: 'check', text: 'Tecnología y software de última generación' },
              ].map((item) => (
                <div class="about-feature-item">
                  <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="feature-check">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span>{item.text}</span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Decoration badge -->
          <div class="about-badge" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="about-badge__inner">
              <span class="about-badge__number">15+</span>
              <span class="about-badge__label">Años de<br/>Experiencia</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats row -->
        <div class="about-counters">
          {[
            { number: '200', suffix: '+', label: 'Proyectos ejecutados', icon: 'building' },
            { number: '50', suffix: '+', label: 'Profesionales en equipo', icon: 'users' },
            { number: '15', suffix: '+', label: 'Años de trayectoria', icon: 'calendar' },
          ].map((stat) => (
            <div class="about-counter-card">
              <div class="about-counter-card__number">
                <span class="counter-value" data-target={stat.number}>{stat.number}</span>
                <span class="counter-suffix">{stat.suffix}</span>
              </div>
              <p class="about-counter-card__label">{stat.label}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--color-white);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 40%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 60%, rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.8) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Content */
  .about-content {
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Mission/Vision */
  .mv-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .mv-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
  }

  .mv-card:hover {
    transform: translateX(4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .mv-card__icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .mv-card__title {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .mv-card__text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Visual block */
  .about-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-visual__main {
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-visual__inner {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Pattern decoration */
  .about-visual__pattern {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    right: -20px;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200, 168, 75, 0.2) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 20px 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .about-visual__accent-line {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-accent), var(--color-accent-light), transparent);
  }

  /* Feature list */
  .about-feature-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .feature-check {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: rgba(200, 168, 75, 0.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    padding: 3px;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
  }

  /* Badge */
  .about-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -1.5rem;
    right: -1rem;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(200, 168, 75, 0.4);
    animation: floatBadge 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .about-badge__inner {
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .about-badge__number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .about-badge__label {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  @keyframes floatBadge {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(3deg); }
  }

  /* Counter cards */
  .about-counters {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-counter-card {
    padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base), border-color var(--transition-base);
  }

  .about-counter-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about-counter-card__number {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  .counter-value {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .counter-suffix {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .about-counter-card__label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-content {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-badge {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      top: -1rem;
      right: -0.5rem;
    }

    .about-badge__number {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .about-counters {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .counter-value {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
